{"word":"G1301 - διατηρέω - diatēréō - dee-at-ay-reh'-o - Keep","slug":"G1301","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">διατηρέω</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Transliteration: </strong>diatēréō"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Phonetic: </strong>dee-at-ay-reh'-o"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Short Definition: </strong>Keep"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>&#x03B4;&#x03B9;&#x03B1;&#x03C4;&#x03B7;&#x03C1;&#x03B5;&#x0301;&#x03C9; - diate&#x0304;reo&#x0304;</b> - <i>dee-at-ay-reh'-o</i><p/>From <a href=\"#/G1223\">G1223</a> and <a href=\"#/G5083\">G5083</a>; to <i>watch thoroughly</i>, that is, (positively and transitively) to <i>observe</i> strictly, or (negatively and reflexively) to <i>avoid</i> wholly: - keep."},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Cognate:</strong> <a href=\"#/G3906\">G3906</a>, <a href=\"#/G3907\">G3907</a>, <a href=\"#/G4933\">G4933</a>, <a href=\"#/G5083\">G5083</a>, <a href=\"#/G5084\">G5084</a>"}]}